name: City Views | Air Canada Airbus A320-200 Dusk Arrival at Calgary Airport
description:
Calgary is gorgeous at night! Here we have my arrival from my DC trip last summer on Air Canada Flight 323 from Montreal, descending, overflying the city with a great view of downtown, and landing on 35R at dusk. It was a great flight as usual with AC, hope you enjoy this arrival video into my hometown!

Thanks for watching!

-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-=-

Airline: Air Canada (ACA/AC)
Aircraft: Airbus A320-214 (A320)
Flight Number: ACA323

Aircraft Name: None

Registration: C-FXCD
Route: Montreal-Trudeau (YUL) - Calgary (YYC)
Callsign: Air Canada 323
Runway used: 35R
Date filmed: July 27, 2017
Local time: 2100
